The paper focuses on visual path prediction, which is a task related to computer vision and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep learning framework, which involves training deep neural networks to learn visual representations and spatiotemporal context modeling. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a unified path-planning scheme, which involves making decisions based on the analytic results returned by the deep context models. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) as well as cs.MM (Multimedia).
